var book = {
	"name": "Daniel",
	"numChapters": 12,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In the third year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21739A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21739A\"></sup>the reign of Jehoiakim king of Judah, Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon came to Jerusalem and besieged it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the Lord gave Jehoiakim king of Judah into his hand, with some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21740B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21740B\"></sup>the vessels of the house of God. And he brought them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21740C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21740C\"></sup>the land of Shinar, to the house of his god, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21740D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21740D\"></sup>and placed the vessels in the treasury of his god.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the king commanded Ashpenaz, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21741E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21741E\"></sup>his chief eunuch, to bring some of the people of Israel, both of the royal family and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21741F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21741F\"></sup>the nobility,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>youths without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21742G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21742G\"></sup>blemish, of good appearance and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21742H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21742H\"></sup>skillful in all wisdom, endowed with knowledge, understanding learning, and competent to stand in the king's palace, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21742I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21742I\"></sup>teach them the literature and language of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21742J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21742J\"></sup>Chaldeans.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The king assigned them a daily portion of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21743K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21743K\"></sup>the food that the king ate, and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21743L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21743L\"></sup>the wine that he drank. They were to be educated for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21743M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21743M\"></sup>three years, and at the end of that time they were to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21743N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21743N\"></sup>stand before the king.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Among these were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21744O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21744O\"></sup>Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21744P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21744P\"></sup>Hananiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21744Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21744Q\"></sup>Mishael, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21744R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21744R\"></sup>Azariah of the tribe of Judah.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21745S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21745S\"></sup>the chief of the eunuchs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21745T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21745T\"></sup>gave them names: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21745U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21745U\"></sup>Daniel he called Belteshazzar, Hananiah he called Shadrach, Mishael he called Meshach, and Azariah he called Abednego.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But Daniel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21746V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21746V\"></sup>resolved that he would not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21746W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21746W\"></sup>defile himself with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21746X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21746X\"></sup>the king's food, or with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21746Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21746Y\"></sup>the wine that he drank. Therefore he asked the chief of the eunuchs to allow him not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21746Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21746Z\"></sup>defile himself.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21747AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21747AA\"></sup>And God gave Daniel favor and compassion in the sight of the chief of the eunuchs,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and the chief of the eunuchs said to Daniel, “I fear my lord the king, who assigned your food and your drink; for why should he see that you were in worse condition than the youths who are of your own age? So you would endanger my head with the king.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then Daniel said to the steward whom the chief of the eunuchs had assigned over Daniel, Hananiah, Mishael, and Azariah,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Test your servants for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21750AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21750AB\"></sup>ten days; let us be given vegetables to eat and water to drink.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then let our appearance and the appearance of the youths who eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21751AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21751AC\"></sup>the king's food be observed by you, and deal with your servants according to what you see.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So he listened to them in this matter, and tested them for ten days.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>At the end of ten days it was seen that they were better in appearance and fatter in flesh than all the youths who ate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21753AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21753AD\"></sup>the king's food.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21754AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21754AE\"></sup>So the steward took away their food and the wine they were to drink, and gave them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21754AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21754AF\"></sup>vegetables.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As for these four youths, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21755AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21755AG\"></sup>God gave them learning and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21755AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21755AH\"></sup>skill in all literature and wisdom, and Daniel had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21755AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21755AI\"></sup>understanding in all visions and dreams.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>At the end of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21756AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21756AJ\"></sup>the time, when the king had commanded that they should be brought in, the chief of the eunuchs brought them in before Nebuchadnezzar.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And the king spoke with them, and among all of them none was found like Daniel, Hananiah, Mishael, and Azariah. Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21757AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21757AK\"></sup>they stood before the king.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And in every matter of wisdom and understanding about which the king inquired of them, he found them ten times better than all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21758AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21758AL\"></sup>the magicians and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21758AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21758AM\"></sup>enchanters that were in all his kingdom.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And Daniel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21759AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21759AN\"></sup>was there until the first year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21759AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21759AO\"></sup>King Cyrus."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>In the second year of the reign of Nebuchadnezzar, Nebuchadnezzar had dreams; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21760A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21760A\"></sup>his spirit was troubled, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21760B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21760B\"></sup>his sleep left him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then the king commanded that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21761C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21761C\"></sup>the magicians, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21761D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21761D\"></sup>the enchanters, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21761E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21761E\"></sup>sorcerers, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21761F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21761F\"></sup>the Chaldeans be summoned to tell the king his dreams. So they came in and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21761G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21761G\"></sup>stood before the king.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the king said to them, “I had a dream, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21762H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21762H\"></sup>my spirit is troubled to know the dream.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21763I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21763I\"></sup>the Chaldeans said to the king in Aramaic, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21763J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21763J\"></sup>“O king, live forever! Tell your servants the dream, and we will show the interpretation.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The king answered and said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21764K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21764K\"></sup>the Chaldeans, “The word from me is firm: if you do not make known to me the dream and its interpretation, you shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21764L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21764L\"></sup>torn limb from limb, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21764M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21764M\"></sup>and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21764N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21764N\"></sup>houses shall be laid in ruins.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But if you show the dream and its interpretation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21765O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21765O\"></sup>you shall receive from me gifts and rewards and great honor. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21765P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21765P\"></sup>Therefore show me the dream and its interpretation.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They answered a second time and said, “Let the king tell his servants the dream, and we will show its interpretation.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The king answered and said, “I know with certainty that you are trying to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21767Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21767Q\"></sup>gain time, because you see that the word from me is firm—",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>if you do not make the dream known to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21768R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21768R\"></sup>there is but one sentence for you. You have agreed to speak lying and corrupt words before me till <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21768S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21768S\"></sup>the times change. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21768T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21768T\"></sup>Therefore tell me the dream, and I shall know that you can show me its interpretation.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21769U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21769U\"></sup>The Chaldeans answered the king and said, “There is not a man on earth who can meet the king's demand, for no great and powerful king has asked such a thing of any magician or enchanter or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21769V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21769V\"></sup>Chaldean.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The thing that the king asks is difficult, and no one can show it to the king except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21770W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21770W\"></sup>the gods, whose dwelling is not with flesh.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Because of this the king was angry and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21771X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21771X\"></sup>very furious, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21771Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21771Y\"></sup>commanded that all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21771Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21771Z\"></sup>the wise men of Babylon be destroyed.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So the decree went out, and the wise men were about to be killed; and they sought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21772AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21772AA\"></sup>Daniel and his companions, to kill them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then Daniel replied with prudence and discretion to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21773AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21773AB\"></sup>Arioch, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21773AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21773AC\"></sup>captain of the king's guard, who had gone out to kill the wise men of Babylon.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He declared to Arioch, the king's captain, “Why is the decree of the king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21774AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21774AD\"></sup>so urgent?” Then Arioch made the matter known to Daniel.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And Daniel went in and requested the king to appoint him a time, that he might show the interpretation to the king.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then Daniel went to his house and made the matter known to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21776AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21776AE\"></sup>Hananiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21776AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21776AF\"></sup>Mishael, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21776AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21776AG\"></sup>Azariah, his companions,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21777AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21777AH\"></sup>and told them to seek mercy from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21777AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21777AI\"></sup>God of heaven concerning this mystery, so that Daniel and his companions might not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21777AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21777AJ\"></sup>be destroyed with the rest of the wise men of Babylon.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the mystery was revealed to Daniel in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21778AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21778AK\"></sup>a vision of the night. Then Daniel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21778AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21778AL\"></sup>blessed the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21778AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21778AM\"></sup>God of heaven.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Daniel answered and said:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21779AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21779AN\"></sup>“Blessed be the name of God forever and ever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21779AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21779AO\"></sup>to whom belong wisdom and might.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21780AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21780AP\"></sup>He changes times and seasons;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21780AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21780AQ\"></sup>he removes kings and sets up kings;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21780AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21780AR\"></sup>he gives wisdom to the wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21780AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21780AS\"></sup>and knowledge to those who have understanding;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21781AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21781AT\"></sup>he reveals deep and hidden things;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21781AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21781AU\"></sup>he knows what is in the darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21781AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21781AV\"></sup>and the light dwells with him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>To you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21782AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21782AW\"></sup>God of my fathers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21782AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21782AX\"></sup>I give thanks and praise,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21782AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21782AY\"></sup>you have given me wisdom and might,and have now made known to me what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21782AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21782AZ\"></sup>we asked of you,for you have made known to us the king's matter.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore Daniel went in to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21783BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21783BA\"></sup>Arioch, whom the king had appointed to destroy the wise men of Babylon. He went and said thus to him: “Do not destroy the wise men of Babylon; bring me in before the king, and I will show the king the interpretation.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21784BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21784BB\"></sup>Arioch brought in Daniel before the king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21784BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21784BC\"></sup>in haste and said thus to him: “I have found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21784BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21784BD\"></sup>among the exiles from Judah a man who will make known to the king the interpretation.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The king declared to Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21785BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21785BE\"></sup>whose name was Belteshazzar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21785BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21785BF\"></sup>“Are you able to make known to me the dream that I have seen and its interpretation?”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Daniel answered the king and said, “No wise men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21786BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21786BG\"></sup>enchanters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21786BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21786BH\"></sup>magicians, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21786BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21786BI\"></sup>astrologers can show to the king the mystery that the king has asked,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21787BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21787BJ\"></sup>there is a God in heaven who reveals mysteries, and he has made known to King Nebuchadnezzar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21787BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21787BK\"></sup>what will be in the latter days. Your dream and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21787BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21787BL\"></sup>the visions of your head as you lay in bed are these:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>To you, O king, as you lay in bed came thoughts of what would be after this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21788BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21788BM\"></sup>and he who reveals mysteries made known to you what is to be.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21789BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21789BN\"></sup>as for me, this mystery has been revealed to me, not because of any wisdom that I have more than all the living, but in order that the interpretation may be made known to the king, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21789BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21789BO\"></sup>you may know the thoughts of your mind.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“You saw, O king, and behold, a great image. This image, mighty and of exceeding brightness, stood before you, and its appearance was frightening.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21791BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21791BP\"></sup>The head of this image was of fine gold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21791BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21791BQ\"></sup>its chest and arms of silver, its middle and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21791BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21791BR\"></sup>thighs of bronze,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21792BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21792BS\"></sup>its legs of iron, its feet partly of iron and partly of clay.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>As you looked, a stone was cut out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21793BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21793BT\"></sup>by no human hand, and it struck the image on its feet of iron and clay, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21793BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21793BU\"></sup>broke them in pieces.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then the iron, the clay, the bronze, the silver, and the gold, all together were broken in pieces, and became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21794BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21794BV\"></sup>like the chaff of the summer threshing floors; and the wind carried them away, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21794BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21794BW\"></sup>not a trace of them could be found. But the stone that struck the image became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21794BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21794BX\"></sup>a great mountain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21794BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21794BY\"></sup>and filled the whole earth.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“This was the dream. Now we will tell the king its interpretation.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>You, O king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21796BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21796BZ\"></sup>the king of kings, to whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21796CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21796CA\"></sup>the God of heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21796CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21796CB\"></sup>has given the kingdom, the power, and the might, and the glory,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>and into whose hand he has given, wherever they dwell, the children of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21797CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21797CC\"></sup>the beasts of the field, and the birds of the heavens, making you rule over them all—you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21797CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21797CD\"></sup>the head of gold.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21798CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21798CE\"></sup>Another kingdom inferior to you shall arise after you, and yet a third kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21798CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21798CF\"></sup>of bronze, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21798CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21798CG\"></sup>which shall rule over all the earth.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21799CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21799CH\"></sup>there shall be a fourth kingdom, strong as iron, because iron <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21799CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21799CI\"></sup>breaks to pieces and shatters all things. And like iron that crushes, it shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21799CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21799CJ\"></sup>break and crush all these.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And as you saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21800CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21800CK\"></sup>the feet and toes, partly of potter's clay and partly of iron, it shall be a divided kingdom, but some of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21800CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21800CL\"></sup>firmness of iron shall be in it, just as you saw iron mixed with the soft clay.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And as the toes of the feet were partly iron and partly clay, so the kingdom shall be partly strong and partly brittle.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>As you saw the iron mixed with soft clay, so they will mix with one another in marriage, but they will not hold together, just as iron does not mix with clay.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And in the days of those kings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21803CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21803CM\"></sup>the God of heaven will set up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21803CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21803CN\"></sup>a kingdom that shall never be destroyed, nor shall the kingdom be left to another people. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21803CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21803CO\"></sup>It shall break in pieces all these kingdoms and bring them to an end, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21803CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21803CP\"></sup>it shall stand forever,",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21804CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21804CQ\"></sup>you saw that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21804CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21804CR\"></sup>a stone was cut from a mountain by no human hand, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21804CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21804CS\"></sup>it broke in pieces the iron, the bronze, the clay, the silver, and the gold. A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21804CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21804CT\"></sup>great God has made known to the king what shall be after this. The dream is certain, and its interpretation sure.”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Then King Nebuchadnezzar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21805CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21805CU\"></sup>fell upon his face and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21805CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21805CV\"></sup>paid homage to Daniel, and commanded that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21805CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21805CW\"></sup>an offering and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21805CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21805CX\"></sup>incense be offered up to him.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>The king answered and said to Daniel, “Truly, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21806CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21806CY\"></sup>God is God of gods and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21806CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21806CZ\"></sup>Lord of kings, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21806DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21806DA\"></sup>a revealer of mysteries, for you have been able to reveal this mystery.”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Then the king gave Daniel high honors and many great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21807DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21807DB\"></sup>gifts, and made him ruler over the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21807DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21807DC\"></sup>province of Babylon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21807DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21807DD\"></sup>chief prefect over all the wise men of Babylon.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Daniel made a request of the king, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21808DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21808DE\"></sup>appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21808DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21808DF\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego over the affairs of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21808DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21808DG\"></sup>the province of Babylon. But Daniel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21808DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21808DH\"></sup>remained at the king's court."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>King Nebuchadnezzar made an image of gold, whose height was sixty cubits and its breadth six cubits. He set it up on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21809A\"></sup>the plain of Dura, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21809B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21809B\"></sup>the province of Babylon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then King Nebuchadnezzar sent to gather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21810C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21810C\"></sup>the satraps, the prefects, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21810D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21810D\"></sup>the governors, the counselors, the treasurers, the justices, the magistrates, and all the officials of the provinces to come to the dedication of the image that King Nebuchadnezzar had set up.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21811E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21811E\"></sup>the satraps, the prefects, and the governors, the counselors, the treasurers, the justices, the magistrates, and all the officials of the provinces gathered for the dedication of the image that King Nebuchadnezzar had set up. And they stood before the image that Nebuchadnezzar had set up.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the herald <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21812F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21812F\"></sup>proclaimed aloud, “You are commanded, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21812G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21812G\"></sup>peoples, nations, and languages,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>that when you hear the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21813H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21813H\"></sup>sound of the horn, pipe, lyre, trigon, harp, bagpipe, and every kind of music, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21813I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21813I\"></sup>are to fall down and worship the golden image that King Nebuchadnezzar has set up.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And whoever does not fall down and worship shall immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21814J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21814J\"></sup>be cast into a burning fiery furnace.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, as soon as all the peoples heard the sound of the horn, pipe, lyre, trigon, harp, bagpipe, and every kind of music, all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21815K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21815K\"></sup>the peoples, nations, and languages fell down and worshiped the golden image that King Nebuchadnezzar had set up.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore at that time certain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21816L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21816L\"></sup>Chaldeans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21816M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21816M\"></sup>came forward and maliciously accused the Jews.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They declared to King Nebuchadnezzar, “O king, live forever!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You, O king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21818N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21818N\"></sup>have made a decree, that every man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21818O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21818O\"></sup>hears the sound of the horn, pipe, lyre, trigon, harp, bagpipe, and every kind of music, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21818P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21818P\"></sup>shall fall down and worship the golden image.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And whoever does not fall down and worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21819Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21819Q\"></sup>shall be cast into a burning fiery furnace.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>There are certain Jews whom you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21820R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21820R\"></sup>appointed over the affairs of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21820S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21820S\"></sup>the province of Babylon: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21820T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21820T\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego. These men, O king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21820U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21820U\"></sup>pay no attention to you; they do not serve your gods or worship the golden image that you have set up.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Nebuchadnezzar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21821V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21821V\"></sup>in furious rage commanded that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21821W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21821W\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego be brought. So they brought these men before the king.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Nebuchadnezzar answered and said to them, “Is it true, O Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego, that you do not serve my gods or worship the golden image that I have set up?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now if you are ready when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21823X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21823X\"></sup>you hear the sound of the horn, pipe, lyre, trigon, harp, bagpipe, and every kind of music, to fall down and worship the image that I have made, well and good. But if you do not worship, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21823Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21823Y\"></sup>you shall immediately be cast into a burning fiery furnace. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21823Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21823Z\"></sup>who is the god who will deliver you out of my hands?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21824AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21824AA\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego answered and said to the king, “O Nebuchadnezzar, we have no need to answer you in this matter.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If this be so, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21825AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21825AB\"></sup>our God whom we serve is able to deliver us from the burning fiery furnace, and he will deliver us out of your hand, O king.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But if not, be it known to you, O king, that we will not serve your gods or worship the golden image that you have set up.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then Nebuchadnezzar was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21827AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21827AC\"></sup>filled with fury, and the expression of his face <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21827AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21827AD\"></sup>was changed against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21827AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21827AE\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego. He ordered the furnace heated seven times more than it was usually heated.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he ordered some of the mighty men of his army <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21828AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21828AF\"></sup>to bind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21828AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21828AG\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego, and to cast them into the burning fiery furnace.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then these men were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21829AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21829AH\"></sup>bound in their cloaks, their tunics, their hats, and their other garments, and they were thrown into the burning fiery furnace.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Because the king's order was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21830AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21830AI\"></sup>urgent and the furnace overheated, the flame of the fire killed those men who took up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21830AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21830AJ\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And these three men, Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego, fell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21831AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21831AK\"></sup>bound into the burning fiery furnace.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then King Nebuchadnezzar was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21832AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21832AL\"></sup>astonished and rose up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21832AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21832AM\"></sup>in haste. He declared to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21832AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21832AN\"></sup>counselors, “Did we not cast three men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21832AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21832AO\"></sup>bound into the fire?” They answered and said to the king, “True, O king.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He answered and said, “But I see four men unbound, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21833AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21833AP\"></sup>walking in the midst of the fire, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21833AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21833AQ\"></sup>are not hurt; and the appearance of the fourth is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21833AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21833AR\"></sup>a son of the gods.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then Nebuchadnezzar came near to the door of the burning fiery furnace; he declared, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21834AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21834AS\"></sup>“Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego, servants of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21834AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21834AT\"></sup>Most High God, come out, and come here!” Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21834AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21834AU\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego came out from the fire.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21835AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21835AV\"></sup>satraps, the prefects, the governors, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21835AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21835AW\"></sup>the king's counselors gathered together and saw that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21835AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21835AX\"></sup>the fire had not had any power over the bodies of those men. The hair of their heads was not singed, their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21835AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21835AY\"></sup>cloaks were not harmed, and no smell of fire had come upon them.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Nebuchadnezzar answered and said, “Blessed be the God of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21836AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21836AZ\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21836BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21836BA\"></sup>has sent his angel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21836BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21836BB\"></sup>delivered his servants, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21836BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21836BC\"></sup>trusted in him, and set aside the king's command, and yielded up their bodies rather than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21836BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21836BD\"></sup>serve and worship any god except their own God.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21837BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21837BE\"></sup>I make a decree: Any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21837BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21837BF\"></sup>people, nation, or language that speaks anything against the God of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21837BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21837BG\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21837BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21837BH\"></sup>shall be torn limb from limb, and their houses laid in ruins, for there is no other god who is able to rescue in this way.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then the king promoted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21838BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21838BI\"></sup>Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21838BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21838BJ\"></sup>the province of Babylon."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span> King Nebuchadnezzar to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21839A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21839A\"></sup>peoples, nations, and languages, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21839B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21839B\"></sup>that dwell in all the earth: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21839C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21839C\"></sup>Peace be multiplied to you!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It has seemed good to me to show the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21840D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21840D\"></sup>signs and wonders that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21840E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21840E\"></sup>Most High God has done for me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>How great are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21841F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21841F\"></sup>his signs,how mighty his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21841G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21841G\"></sup>wonders!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21841H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21841H\"></sup>His kingdom is an everlasting kingdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21841I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21841I\"></sup>and his dominion endures from generation to generation.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup> I, Nebuchadnezzar, was at ease in my house and prospering in my palace.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I saw a dream that made me afraid. As I lay in bed the fancies and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21843J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21843J\"></sup>the visions of my head alarmed me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21844K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21844K\"></sup>I made a decree that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21844L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21844L\"></sup>all the wise men of Babylon should be brought before me, that they might make known to me the interpretation of the dream.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21845M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21845M\"></sup>the magicians, the enchanters, the Chaldeans, and the astrologers came in, and I told them the dream, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21845N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21845N\"></sup>they could not make known to me its interpretation.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>At last Daniel came in before me—he who was named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21846O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21846O\"></sup>Belteshazzar after the name of my god, and in whom is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21846P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21846P\"></sup>the spirit of the holy gods—and I told him the dream, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“O Belteshazzar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21847Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21847Q\"></sup>chief of the magicians, because I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21847R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21847R\"></sup>the spirit of the holy gods is in you and that no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21847S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21847S\"></sup>mystery is too difficult for you, tell me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21847T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21847T\"></sup>the visions of my dream that I saw and their interpretation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21848U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21848U\"></sup>The visions of my head as I lay in bed were these: I saw, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21848V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21848V\"></sup>behold, a tree in the midst of the earth, and its height was great.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21849W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21849W\"></sup>The tree grew and became strong, and its top reached to heaven, and it was visible to the end of the whole earth.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21850X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21850X\"></sup>Its leaves were beautiful and its fruit abundant, and in it was food for all. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21850Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21850Y\"></sup>The beasts of the field found shade under it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21850Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21850Z\"></sup>the birds of the heavens lived in its branches, and all flesh was fed from it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I saw in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21851AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21851AA\"></sup>the visions of my head as I lay in bed, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21851AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21851AB\"></sup>a watcher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21851AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21851AC\"></sup>a holy one, came down from heaven.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21852AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21852AD\"></sup>proclaimed aloud and said thus: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21852AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21852AE\"></sup>‘Chop down the tree and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21852AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21852AF\"></sup>lop off its branches, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21852AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21852AG\"></sup>strip off its leaves and scatter its fruit. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21852AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21852AH\"></sup>Let the beasts flee from under it and the birds from its branches.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But leave the stump of its roots in the earth, bound with a band of iron and bronze, amid the tender grass of the field. Let him be wet with the dew of heaven. Let his portion be with the beasts in the grass of the earth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let his mind be changed from a man's, and let a beast's mind be given to him; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21854AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21854AI\"></sup>and let seven periods of time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21854AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21854AJ\"></sup>pass over him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The sentence is by the decree of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21855AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21855AK\"></sup>the watchers, the decision by the word of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21855AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21855AL\"></sup>the holy ones, to the end that the living may know that the Most High <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21855AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21855AM\"></sup>rules the kingdom of men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21855AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21855AN\"></sup>and gives it to whom he will and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21855AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21855AO\"></sup>sets over it the lowliest of men.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This dream I, King Nebuchadnezzar, saw. And you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21856AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21856AP\"></sup>Belteshazzar, tell me the interpretation, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21856AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21856AQ\"></sup>all the wise men of my kingdom are not able to make known to me the interpretation, but you are able, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21856AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21856AR\"></sup>the spirit of the holy gods is in you.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then Daniel, whose name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21857AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21857AS\"></sup>Belteshazzar, was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21857AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21857AT\"></sup>dismayed for a while, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21857AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21857AU\"></sup>his thoughts alarmed him. The king answered and said, “Belteshazzar, let not the dream or the interpretation alarm you.” Belteshazzar answered and said, “My lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21857AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21857AV\"></sup>may the dream be for those who hate you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21857AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21857AW\"></sup>and its interpretation for your enemies!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21858AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21858AX\"></sup>The tree you saw, which grew and became strong, so that its top reached to heaven, and it was visible to the end of the whole earth,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21859AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21859AY\"></sup>whose leaves were beautiful and its fruit abundant, and in which was food for all, under which beasts of the field found shade, and in whose branches the birds of the heavens lived—",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21860AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21860AZ\"></sup>it is you, O king, who have grown and become strong. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21860BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21860BA\"></sup>Your greatness has grown and reaches to heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21860BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21860BB\"></sup>and your dominion to the ends of the earth.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And because the king saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21861BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21861BC\"></sup>a watcher, a holy one, coming down from heaven and saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21861BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21861BD\"></sup>‘Chop down the tree and destroy it, but leave the stump of its roots in the earth, bound with a band of iron and bronze, in the tender grass of the field, and let him be wet with the dew of heaven, and let his portion be with the beasts of the field, till <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21861BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21861BE\"></sup>seven periods of time pass over him,’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>this is the interpretation, O king: It is a decree of the Most High, which has come upon my lord the king,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21863BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21863BF\"></sup>that you shall be driven from among men, and your dwelling shall be with the beasts of the field. You shall be made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21863BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21863BG\"></sup>to eat grass like an ox, and you shall be wet with the dew of heaven, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21863BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21863BH\"></sup>seven periods of time shall pass over you, till <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21863BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21863BI\"></sup>you know that the Most High rules the kingdom of men and gives it to whom he will.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And as it was commanded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21864BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21864BJ\"></sup>to leave the stump of the roots of the tree, your kingdom shall be confirmed for you from the time that you know that Heaven rules.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Therefore, O king, let my counsel be acceptable to you: break off your sins by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21865BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21865BK\"></sup>practicing righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21865BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21865BL\"></sup>and your iniquities by showing mercy to the oppressed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21865BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21865BM\"></sup>that there may perhaps be a lengthening of your prosperity.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>All this came upon King Nebuchadnezzar.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At the end of twelve months he was walking on the roof of the royal palace of Babylon,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>and the king answered and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21868BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21868BN\"></sup>“Is not this great Babylon, which I have built by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21868BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21868BO\"></sup>my mighty power as a royal residence and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21868BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21868BP\"></sup>the glory of my majesty?”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21869BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21869BQ\"></sup>While the words were still in the king's mouth, there fell a voice from heaven, “O King Nebuchadnezzar, to you it is spoken: The kingdom has departed from you,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21870BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21870BR\"></sup>and you shall be driven from among men, and your dwelling shall be with the beasts of the field. And you shall be made to eat grass like an ox, and seven periods of time shall pass over you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21870BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21870BS\"></sup>until you know that the Most High rules the kingdom of men and gives it to whom he will.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Immediately the word was fulfilled against Nebuchadnezzar. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21871BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21871BT\"></sup>He was driven from among men and ate grass like an ox, and his body was wet with the dew of heaven till his hair grew as long as eagles' feathers, and his nails were like birds' claws.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21872BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21872BU\"></sup>At the end of the days I, Nebuchadnezzar, lifted my eyes to heaven, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21872BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21872BV\"></sup>my reason returned to me, and I blessed the Most High, and praised and honored <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21872BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21872BW\"></sup>him who lives forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21872BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21872BX\"></sup>for his dominion is an everlasting dominion,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21872BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21872BY\"></sup>his kingdom endures from generation to generation;",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21873BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21873BZ\"></sup>all the inhabitants of the earth are accounted as nothing,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21873CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21873CA\"></sup>he does according to his will among the host of heavenand among the inhabitants of the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21873CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21873CB\"></sup>and none can stay his handor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21873CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21873CC\"></sup>say to him, “What have you done?”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>At the same time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21874CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21874CD\"></sup>my reason returned to me, and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21874CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21874CE\"></sup>the glory of my kingdom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21874CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21874CF\"></sup>my majesty and splendor returned to me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21874CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21874CG\"></sup>My counselors and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21874CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21874CH\"></sup>my lords sought me, and I was established in my kingdom, and still more greatness was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21874CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21874CI\"></sup>added to me.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Now I, Nebuchadnezzar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21875CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21875CJ\"></sup>praise and extol and honor the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21875CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21875CK\"></sup>King of heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21875CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21875CL\"></sup>for all his works are right and his ways are just; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21875CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21875CM\"></sup>those who walk in pride he is able to humble."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21876A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21876A\"></sup>King Belshazzar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21876B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21876B\"></sup>made a great feast for a thousand of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21876C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21876C\"></sup>lords and drank wine in front of the thousand.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21877D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21877D\"></sup>Belshazzar, when he tasted the wine, commanded that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21877E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21877E\"></sup>the vessels of gold and of silver that Nebuchadnezzar his father had taken out of the temple in Jerusalem be brought, that the king and his lords, his wives, and his concubines might drink from them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then they brought in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21878F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21878F\"></sup>the golden vessels that had been taken out of the temple, the house of God in Jerusalem, and the king and his lords, his wives, and his concubines drank from them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They drank wine and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21879G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21879G\"></sup>praised the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21879H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21879H\"></sup>gods of gold and silver, bronze, iron, wood, and stone.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21880I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21880I\"></sup>Immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21880J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21880J\"></sup>the fingers of a human hand appeared and wrote on the plaster of the wall of the king's palace, opposite the lampstand. And the king saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21880K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21880K\"></sup>the hand as it wrote.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21881L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21881L\"></sup>Then the king's color changed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21881M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21881M\"></sup>and his thoughts alarmed him; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21881N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21881N\"></sup>his limbs gave way, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21881O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21881O\"></sup>his knees knocked together.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21882P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21882P\"></sup>The king called loudly to bring in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21882Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21882Q\"></sup>the enchanters, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21882R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21882R\"></sup>Chaldeans, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21882S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21882S\"></sup>the astrologers. The king declared to the wise men of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21882T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21882T\"></sup>“Whoever reads this writing, and shows me its interpretation, shall be clothed with purple and have a chain of gold around his neck and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21882U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21882U\"></sup>shall be the third ruler in the kingdom.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then all the king's wise men came in, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21883V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21883V\"></sup>they could not read the writing or make known to the king the interpretation.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then King Belshazzar was greatly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21884W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21884W\"></sup>alarmed, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21884X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21884X\"></sup>color changed, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21884Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21884Y\"></sup>lords were perplexed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The queen, because of the words of the king and his lords, came into the banqueting hall, and the queen declared, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21885Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21885Z\"></sup>“O king, live forever! Let not your thoughts alarm you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21885AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21885AA\"></sup>or your color change.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There is a man in your kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21886AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21886AB\"></sup>in whom is the spirit of the holy gods. In the days of your father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21886AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21886AC\"></sup>light and understanding and wisdom like the wisdom of the gods were found in him, and King Nebuchadnezzar, your father—your father the king—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21886AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21886AD\"></sup>made him chief of the magicians, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21886AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21886AE\"></sup>enchanters, Chaldeans, and astrologers,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21887AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21887AF\"></sup>because an excellent spirit, knowledge, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21887AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21887AG\"></sup>understanding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21887AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21887AH\"></sup>to interpret dreams, explain riddles, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21887AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21887AI\"></sup>solve problems were found in this Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21887AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21887AJ\"></sup>whom the king named Belteshazzar. Now let Daniel be called, and he will show the interpretation.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Daniel was brought in before the king. The king answered and said to Daniel, “You are that Daniel, one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21888AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21888AK\"></sup>the exiles of Judah, whom the king my father brought from Judah.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have heard of you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21889AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21889AL\"></sup>the spirit of the gods is in you, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21889AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21889AM\"></sup>light and understanding and excellent wisdom are found in you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21890AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21890AN\"></sup>the wise men, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21890AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21890AO\"></sup>enchanters, have been brought in before me to read this writing and make known to me its interpretation, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21890AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21890AP\"></sup>they could not show the interpretation of the matter.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21891AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21891AQ\"></sup>But I have heard that you can give interpretations and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21891AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21891AR\"></sup>solve problems. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21891AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21891AS\"></sup>Now if you can read the writing and make known to me its interpretation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21891AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21891AT\"></sup>you shall be clothed with purple and have a chain of gold around your neck and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21891AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21891AU\"></sup>shall be the third ruler in the kingdom.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then Daniel answered and said before the king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21892AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21892AV\"></sup>“Let your gifts be for yourself, and give your rewards to another. Nevertheless, I will read the writing to the king and make known to him the interpretation.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>O king, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21893AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21893AW\"></sup>Most High God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21893AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21893AX\"></sup>gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21893AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21893AY\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar your father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21893AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21893AZ\"></sup>kingship and greatness and glory and majesty.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And because of the greatness that he gave him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21894BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21894BA\"></sup>all peoples, nations, and languages <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21894BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21894BB\"></sup>trembled and feared before him. Whom he would, he killed, and whom he would, he kept alive; whom he would, he raised up, and whom he would, he humbled.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21895BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21895BC\"></sup>when his heart was lifted up and his spirit was hardened so that he dealt proudly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21895BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21895BD\"></sup>he was brought down from his kingly throne, and his glory was taken from him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21896BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21896BE\"></sup>He was driven from among the children of mankind, and his mind was made like that of a beast, and his dwelling was with the wild donkeys. He was fed grass like an ox, and his body was wet with the dew of heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21896BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21896BF\"></sup>until he knew that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21896BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21896BG\"></sup>Most High God rules the kingdom of mankind and sets over it whom he will.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And you his son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21897BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21897BH\"></sup>Belshazzar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21897BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21897BI\"></sup>have not humbled your heart, though you knew all this,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>but you have lifted up yourself against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21898BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21898BJ\"></sup>the Lord of heaven. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21898BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21898BK\"></sup>the vessels of his house have been brought in before you, and you and your lords, your wives, and your concubines have drunk wine from them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21898BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21898BL\"></sup>And you have praised the gods of silver and gold, of bronze, iron, wood, and stone, which do not see or hear or know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21898BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21898BM\"></sup>but the God in whose hand is your breath, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21898BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21898BN\"></sup>whose are all your ways, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21898BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21898BO\"></sup>you have not honored.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Then from his presence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21899BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21899BP\"></sup>the hand was sent, and this writing was inscribed.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And this is the writing that was inscribed: <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Mene</span>, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Mene</span>, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Tekel</span>, and <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Parsin</span>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>This is the interpretation of the matter: <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Mene</span>, God has numbered the days of your kingdom and brought it to an end;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Tekel</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21902BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21902BQ\"></sup>you have been weighed in the balances and found wanting;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Peres</span>, your kingdom is divided and given to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21903BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21903BR\"></sup>the Medes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21903BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21903BS\"></sup>Persians.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21904BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21904BT\"></sup>Belshazzar gave the command, and Daniel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21904BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21904BU\"></sup>was clothed with purple, a chain of gold was put around his neck, and a proclamation was made about him, that he should be the third ruler in the kingdom.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21905BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21905BV\"></sup>That very night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21905BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21905BW\"></sup>Belshazzar the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21905BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21905BX\"></sup>Chaldean king was killed.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup> And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21906BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21906BY\"></sup>Darius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21906BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21906BZ\"></sup>the Mede received the kingdom, being about sixty-two years old."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>It pleased Darius to set over the kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21907A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21907A\"></sup>120 <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21907B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21907B\"></sup>satraps, to be throughout the whole kingdom;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and over them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21908C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21908C\"></sup>three high officials, of whom Daniel was one, to whom these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21908D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21908D\"></sup>satraps should give account, so that the king might suffer no loss.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then this Daniel became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21909E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21909E\"></sup>distinguished above all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21909F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21909F\"></sup>the other high officials and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21909G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21909G\"></sup>satraps, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21909H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21909H\"></sup>an excellent spirit was in him. And the king planned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21909I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21909I\"></sup>to set him over the whole kingdom.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21910J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21910J\"></sup>the high officials and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21910K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21910K\"></sup>the satraps <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21910L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21910L\"></sup>sought to find a ground for complaint against Daniel with regard to the kingdom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21910M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21910M\"></sup>but they could find no ground for complaint or any fault, because he was faithful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21910N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21910N\"></sup>and no error or fault was found in him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then these men said, “We shall not find any ground for complaint against this Daniel unless we find it in connection with the law of his God.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21912O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21912O\"></sup>high officials and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21912P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21912P\"></sup>satraps came by agreement to the king and said to him, “O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21912Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21912Q\"></sup>King Darius, live forever!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21913R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21913R\"></sup>high officials of the kingdom, the prefects and the satraps, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21913S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21913S\"></sup>counselors and the governors are agreed that the king should establish an ordinance and enforce an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21913T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21913T\"></sup>injunction, that whoever makes petition to any god or man for thirty days, except to you, O king, shall be cast into the den of lions.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now, O king, establish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21914U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21914U\"></sup>the injunction and sign the document, so that it cannot be changed, according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21914V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21914V\"></sup>the law of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21914W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21914W\"></sup>the Medes and the Persians, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21914X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21914X\"></sup>which cannot be revoked.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore King Darius signed the document and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21915Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21915Y\"></sup>injunction.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When Daniel knew that the document had been signed, he went to his house where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21916Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21916Z\"></sup>he had windows in his upper chamber open <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21916AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21916AA\"></sup>toward Jerusalem. He got down on his knees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21916AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21916AB\"></sup>three times a day and prayed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21916AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21916AC\"></sup>gave thanks before his God, as he had done previously.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then these men came by agreement and found Daniel making petition and plea before his God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21918AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21918AD\"></sup>came near and said before the king, concerning the injunction, “O king! Did you not sign <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21918AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21918AE\"></sup>an injunction, that anyone who makes petition to any god or man within thirty days except to you, O king, shall be cast into the den of lions?” The king answered and said, “The thing stands fast, according to the law of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21918AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21918AF\"></sup>the Medes and Persians, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21918AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21918AG\"></sup>which cannot be revoked.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then they answered and said before the king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21919AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21919AH\"></sup>“Daniel, who is one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21919AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21919AI\"></sup>of the exiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21919AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21919AJ\"></sup>from Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21919AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21919AK\"></sup>pays no attention to you, O king, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21919AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21919AL\"></sup>the injunction you have signed, but makes his petition <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21919AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21919AM\"></sup>three times a day.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21920AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21920AN\"></sup>the king, when he heard these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21920AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21920AO\"></sup>was much distressed and set his mind to deliver Daniel. And he labored till the sun went down to rescue him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then these men came by agreement to the king and said to the king, “Know, O king, that it is a law of the Medes and Persians that no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21921AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21921AP\"></sup>injunction or ordinance that the king establishes can be changed.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then the king commanded, and Daniel was brought and cast into the den of lions. The king declared to Daniel, “May <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21922AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21922AQ\"></sup>your God, whom you serve continually, deliver you!”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21923AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21923AR\"></sup>And a stone was brought and laid on the mouth of the den, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21923AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21923AS\"></sup>and the king sealed it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21923AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21923AT\"></sup>with his own signet and with the signet of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21923AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21923AU\"></sup>lords, that nothing might be changed concerning Daniel.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then the king went to his palace and spent the night fasting; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21924AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21924AV\"></sup>no diversions were brought to him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21924AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21924AW\"></sup>sleep fled from him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then, at break of day, the king arose and went in haste to the den of lions.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As he came near to the den where Daniel was, he cried out in a tone of anguish. The king declared to Daniel, “O Daniel, servant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21926AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21926AX\"></sup>the living God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21926AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21926AY\"></sup>has your God, whom you serve continually, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21926AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21926AZ\"></sup>been able to deliver you from the lions?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then Daniel said to the king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21927BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21927BA\"></sup>“O king, live forever!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>My God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21928BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21928BB\"></sup>sent his angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21928BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21928BC\"></sup>and shut the lions' mouths, and they have not harmed me, because I was found blameless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21928BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21928BD\"></sup>before him; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21928BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21928BE\"></sup>and also before you, O king, I have done no harm.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then the king was exceedingly glad, and commanded that Daniel be taken up out of the den. So Daniel was taken up out of the den, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21929BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21929BF\"></sup>no kind of harm was found on him, because he had trusted in his God.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And the king commanded, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21930BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21930BG\"></sup>those men who had maliciously accused Daniel were brought and cast into the den of lions—they, their children, and their wives. And before they reached the bottom of the den, the lions overpowered them and broke all their bones in pieces.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Then King Darius wrote to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21931BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21931BH\"></sup>the peoples, nations, and languages <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21931BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21931BI\"></sup>that dwell in all the earth: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21931BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21931BJ\"></sup>“Peace be multiplied to you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21932BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21932BK\"></sup>I make a decree, that in all my royal dominion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21932BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21932BL\"></sup>people are to tremble and fear before the God of Daniel,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21932BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21932BM\"></sup>he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21932BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21932BN\"></sup>the living God,enduring forever;his kingdom shall never be destroyed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21932BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21932BO\"></sup>and his dominion shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21932BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21932BP\"></sup>to the end.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He delivers and rescues;he works <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21933BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21933BQ\"></sup>signs and wondersin heaven and on earth,he who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21933BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21933BR\"></sup>saved Danielfrom the power of the lions.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So this Daniel prospered during the reign of Darius and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21934BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21934BS\"></sup>the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21934BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21934BT\"></sup>Cyrus the Persian."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>In the first year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21935A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21935A\"></sup>Belshazzar king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21935B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21935B\"></sup>Daniel saw a dream and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21935C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21935C\"></sup>visions of his head as he lay in his bed. Then he wrote down the dream and told the sum of the matter.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Daniel declared, “I saw in my vision by night, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21936D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21936D\"></sup>the four winds of heaven were stirring up the great sea.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And four great beasts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21937E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21937E\"></sup>came up out of the sea, different from one another.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The first was like a lion and had eagles' wings. Then as I looked its wings were plucked off, and it was lifted up from the ground and made to stand on two feet like a man, and the mind of a man was given to it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21939F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21939F\"></sup>another beast, a second one, like a bear. It was raised up on one side. It had three ribs in its mouth between its teeth; and it was told, ‘Arise, devour much flesh.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>After this I looked, and behold, another, like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21940G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21940G\"></sup>leopard, with four wings of a bird on its back. And the beast had four heads, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21940H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21940H\"></sup>dominion was given to it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>After this I saw in the night visions, and behold, a fourth beast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21941I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21941I\"></sup>terrifying and dreadful and exceedingly strong. It had great iron teeth; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21941J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21941J\"></sup>it devoured and broke in pieces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21941K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21941K\"></sup>and stamped what was left with its feet. It was different from all the beasts that were before it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21941L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21941L\"></sup>it had ten horns.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I considered the horns, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21942M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21942M\"></sup>there came up among them another horn, a little one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21942N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21942N\"></sup>before which three of the first horns were plucked up by the roots. And behold, in this horn were eyes like the eyes of a man, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21942O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21942O\"></sup>a mouth speaking great things.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“As I looked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21943P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21943P\"></sup>thrones were placed,and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21943Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21943Q\"></sup>Ancient of Days took his seat;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21943R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21943R\"></sup>his clothing was white as snow,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21943S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21943S\"></sup>the hair of his head like pure wool;his throne was fiery flames;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21943T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21943T\"></sup>its wheels were burning fire.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21944U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21944U\"></sup>A stream of fire issuedand came out from before him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21944V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21944V\"></sup>a thousand thousands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21944W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21944W\"></sup>served him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21944X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21944X\"></sup>and ten thousand times ten thousand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21944Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21944Y\"></sup>stood before him;the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21944Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21944Z\"></sup>court sat in judgment,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21944AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21944AA\"></sup>the books were opened.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I looked then because of the sound of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21945AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21945AB\"></sup>the great words that the horn was speaking. And as I looked, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21945AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21945AC\"></sup>the beast was killed, and its body destroyed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21945AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21945AD\"></sup>and given over to be burned with fire.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As for the rest of the beasts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21946AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21946AE\"></sup>their dominion was taken away, but their lives were prolonged for a season and a time.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I saw in the night visions,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21947AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21947AF\"></sup>behold, with the clouds of heaventhere came one like a son of man,and he came to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21947AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21947AG\"></sup>Ancient of Daysand was presented before him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21948AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21948AH\"></sup>And to him was given dominionand glory and a kingdom,that all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21948AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21948AI\"></sup>peoples, nations, and languagesshould serve him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21948AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21948AJ\"></sup>his dominion is an everlasting dominion,which shall not pass away,and his kingdom onethat shall not be destroyed.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“As for me, Daniel, my spirit within me was anxious, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21949AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21949AK\"></sup>the visions of my head alarmed me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I approached one of those who stood there and asked him the truth concerning all this. So he told me and made known to me the interpretation of the things.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21951AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21951AL\"></sup>‘These four great beasts are four kings who shall arise out of the earth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21952AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21952AM\"></sup>the saints of the Most High shall receive the kingdom and possess the kingdom forever, forever and ever.’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Then I desired to know the truth about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21953AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21953AN\"></sup>the fourth beast, which was different from all the rest, exceedingly terrifying, with its teeth of iron and claws of bronze, and which devoured and broke in pieces and stamped what was left with its feet,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21954AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21954AO\"></sup>and about the ten horns that were on its head, and the other horn that came up and before which three of them fell, the horn that had eyes and a mouth that spoke great things, and that seemed greater than its companions.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>As I looked, this horn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21955AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21955AP\"></sup>made war with the saints and prevailed over them,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>until the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21956AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21956AQ\"></sup>Ancient of Days came, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21956AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21956AR\"></sup>judgment was given for the saints of the Most High, and the time came when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21956AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21956AS\"></sup>the saints possessed the kingdom.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Thus he said: ‘As for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21957AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21957AT\"></sup>the fourth beast,there shall be a fourth kingdom on earth,which shall be different from all the kingdoms,and it shall devour the whole earth,and trample it down, and break it to pieces.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>As for the ten horns,out of this kingdom ten kings shall arise,and another shall arise after them;he shall be different from the former ones,and shall put down three kings.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21959AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21959AU\"></sup>He shall speak words against the Most High,and shall wear out the saints of the Most High,and shall think to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21959AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21959AV\"></sup>change the times and the law;and they shall be given into his handfor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21959AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21959AW\"></sup>a time, times, and half a time.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21960AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21960AX\"></sup>But the court shall sit in judgment,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21960AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21960AY\"></sup>his dominion shall be taken away,to be consumed and destroyed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21960AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21960AZ\"></sup>to the end.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21961BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21961BA\"></sup>And the kingdom and the dominionand the greatness of the kingdoms under the whole heavenshall be given to the people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21961BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21961BB\"></sup>the saints of the Most High;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21961BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21961BC\"></sup>his kingdom shall be an everlasting kingdom,and all dominions shall serve and obey him.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Here is the end of the matter. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21962BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21962BD\"></sup>As for me, Daniel, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21962BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21962BE\"></sup>thoughts greatly alarmed me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21962BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21962BF\"></sup>and my color changed, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21962BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21962BG\"></sup>I kept the matter in my heart.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>In the third year of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21963A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21963A\"></sup>King Belshazzar a vision appeared to me, Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21963B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21963B\"></sup>after that which appeared to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21963C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21963C\"></sup>at the first.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw in the vision; and when I saw, I was in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21964D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21964D\"></sup>Susa the citadel, which is in the province of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21964E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21964E\"></sup>Elam. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21964F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21964F\"></sup>I saw in the vision, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21964G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21964G\"></sup>and I was at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21964H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21964H\"></sup>Ulai canal.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I raised my eyes and saw, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21965I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21965I\"></sup>a ram standing on the bank of the canal. It had two horns, and both horns were high, but one was higher than the other, and the higher one came up last.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21966J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21966J\"></sup>the ram charging westward and northward and southward. No <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21966K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21966K\"></sup>beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21966L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21966L\"></sup>could stand before him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21966M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21966M\"></sup>and there was no one who could rescue from his power. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21966N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21966N\"></sup>He did as he pleased and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21966O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21966O\"></sup>became great.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As I was considering, behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21967P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21967P\"></sup>male goat came from the west across the face of the whole earth, without touching the ground. And the goat had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21967Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21967Q\"></sup>a conspicuous horn between his eyes.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21968R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21968R\"></sup>the ram with the two horns, which I had seen standing on the bank of the canal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21968S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21968S\"></sup>and he ran at him in his powerful wrath.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I saw him come close to the ram, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21969T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21969T\"></sup>and he was enraged against him and struck the ram and broke his two horns. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21969U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21969U\"></sup>And the ram had no power to stand before him, but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21969V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21969V\"></sup>cast him down to the ground and trampled on him. And there was no one who could rescue the ram from his power.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21970W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21970W\"></sup>the goat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21970X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21970X\"></sup>became exceedingly great, but when he was strong, the great horn was broken, and instead of it there came up four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21970Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21970Y\"></sup>conspicuous horns toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21970Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21970Z\"></sup>the four winds of heaven.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Out of one of them came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21971AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21971AA\"></sup>a little horn, which grew exceedingly great toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21971AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21971AB\"></sup>the south, toward the east, and toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21971AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21971AC\"></sup>the glorious land.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21972AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21972AD\"></sup>It grew great, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21972AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21972AE\"></sup>even to the host of heaven. And some of the host <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21972AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21972AF\"></sup>and some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21972AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21972AG\"></sup>the stars it threw down to the ground and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21972AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21972AH\"></sup>trampled on them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21973AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21973AI\"></sup>It became great, even as great as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21973AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21973AJ\"></sup>the Prince of the host. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21973AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21973AK\"></sup>And the regular burnt offering was taken away from him, and the place of his sanctuary was overthrown.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And a host will be given over to it together with the regular burnt offering because of transgression, and it will throw truth to the ground, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21974AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21974AL\"></sup>it will act and prosper.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21975AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21975AM\"></sup>a holy one speaking, and another holy one said to the one who spoke, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21975AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21975AN\"></sup>“For how long is the vision concerning the regular burnt offering, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21975AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21975AO\"></sup>the transgression that makes desolate, and the giving over of the sanctuary and host to be trampled underfoot?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he said to me, “For 2,300 <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21976AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21976AP\"></sup>evenings and mornings. Then the sanctuary shall be restored to its rightful state.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When I, Daniel, had seen the vision, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21977AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21977AQ\"></sup>sought to understand it. And behold, there stood before me one having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21977AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21977AR\"></sup>the appearance of a man.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21978AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21978AS\"></sup>And I heard a man's voice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21978AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21978AT\"></sup>between the banks of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21978AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21978AU\"></sup>Ulai, and it called, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21978AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21978AV\"></sup>“Gabriel, make this man understand the vision.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So he came near where I stood. And when he came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21979AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21979AW\"></sup>I was frightened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21979AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21979AX\"></sup>and fell on my face. But he said to me, “Understand, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21979AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21979AY\"></sup>O son of man, that the vision is for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21979AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21979AZ\"></sup>the time of the end.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And when he had spoken to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21980BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21980BA\"></sup>I fell into a deep sleep with my face to the ground. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21980BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21980BB\"></sup>he touched me and made me stand up.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He said, “Behold, I will make known to you what shall be at the latter end of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21981BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21981BC\"></sup>the indignation, for it refers to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21981BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21981BD\"></sup>the appointed time of the end.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21982BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21982BE\"></sup>the ram that you saw with the two horns, these are the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21982BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21982BF\"></sup>Media and Persia.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21983BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21983BG\"></sup>the goat is the king of Greece. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21983BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21983BH\"></sup>the great horn between his eyes is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21983BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21983BI\"></sup>the first king.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21984BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21984BJ\"></sup>As for the horn that was broken, in place of which four others arose, four kingdoms shall arise from his nation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21984BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21984BK\"></sup>but not with his power.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And at the latter end of their kingdom, when the transgressors have reached their limit, a king of bold face, one who understands riddles, shall arise.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>His power shall be great—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21986BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21986BL\"></sup>but not by his own power; and he shall cause fearful destruction <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21986BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21986BM\"></sup>and shall succeed in what he does, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21986BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21986BN\"></sup>and destroy mighty men and the people who are the saints.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21987BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21987BO\"></sup>By his cunning he shall make deceit prosper under his hand, and in his own mind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21987BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21987BP\"></sup>he shall become great. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21987BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21987BQ\"></sup>Without warning he shall destroy many. And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21987BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21987BR\"></sup>shall even rise up against the Prince of princes, and he shall be broken—but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21987BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21987BS\"></sup>by no human hand.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The vision of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21988BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21988BT\"></sup>the evenings and the mornings that has been told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21988BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21988BU\"></sup>is true, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21988BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21988BV\"></sup>seal up the vision, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21988BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21988BW\"></sup>for it refers to many days from now.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21989BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21989BX\"></sup>I, Daniel, was overcome and lay sick for some days. Then I rose and went about the king's business, but I was appalled by the vision <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21989BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21989BY\"></sup>and did not understand it."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21990A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21990A\"></sup>In the first year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21990B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21990B\"></sup>Darius the son of Ahasuerus, by descent a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21990C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21990C\"></sup>Mede, who was made king over the realm of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21990D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21990D\"></sup>Chaldeans—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>in the first year of his reign, I, Daniel, perceived in the books the number of years that, according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21991E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21991E\"></sup>the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Jeremiah the prophet, must pass before the end of the desolations of Jerusalem, namely, seventy years.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then I turned my face to the Lord God, seeking him by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21992F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21992F\"></sup>prayer and pleas for mercy with fasting and sackcloth and ashes.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21993G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21993G\"></sup>made confession, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21993H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21993H\"></sup>“O Lord, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21993I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21993I\"></sup>great and awesome God, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21993J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21993J\"></sup>keeps covenant and steadfast love with those who love him and keep his commandments,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21994K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21994K\"></sup>we have sinned and done wrong and acted wickedly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21994L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21994L\"></sup>and rebelled, turning aside from your commandments and rules.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21995M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21995M\"></sup>We have not listened to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21995N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21995N\"></sup>your servants the prophets, who spoke in your name to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21995O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21995O\"></sup>our kings, our princes, and our fathers, and to all the people of the land.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>To you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21996P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21996P\"></sup>O Lord, belongs righteousness, but to us open shame, as at this day, to the men of Judah, to the inhabitants of Jerusalem, and to all Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21996Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21996Q\"></sup>those who are near and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21996R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21996R\"></sup>those who are far away, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21996S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21996S\"></sup>all the lands to which you have driven them, because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21996T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21996T\"></sup>the treachery that they have committed against you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>To us, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, belongs open shame, to our kings, to our princes, and to our fathers, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21997U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21997U\"></sup>we have sinned against you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21998V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21998V\"></sup>To the Lord our God belong mercy and forgiveness, for we have rebelled against him",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21999W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21999W\"></sup>and have not obeyed the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God by walking in his laws, which he set before us by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-21999X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-21999X\"></sup>his servants the prophets.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22000Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22000Y\"></sup>All Israel has transgressed your law and turned aside, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22000Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22000Z\"></sup>refusing to obey your voice. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22000AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22000AA\"></sup>And the curse and oath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22000AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22000AB\"></sup>that are written in the Law of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22000AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22000AC\"></sup>Moses the servant of God have been poured out upon us, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22000AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22000AD\"></sup>we have sinned against him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He has confirmed his words, which he spoke against us and against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22001AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22001AE\"></sup>our rulers who ruled us, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22001AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22001AF\"></sup>bringing upon us a great calamity. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22001AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22001AG\"></sup>For under the whole heaven there has not been done anything like what has been done against Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22002AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22002AH\"></sup>As it is written in the Law of Moses, all this calamity has come upon us; yet we have not entreated the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22002AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22002AI\"></sup>turning from our iniquities and gaining insight by your truth.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22003AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22003AJ\"></sup>Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has kept ready the calamity and has brought it upon us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22003AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22003AK\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God is righteous in all the works that he has done, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22003AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22003AL\"></sup>we have not obeyed his voice.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And now, O Lord our God, who brought your people out of the land of Egypt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22004AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22004AM\"></sup>with a mighty hand, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22004AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22004AN\"></sup>have made a name for yourself, as at this day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22004AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22004AO\"></sup>we have sinned, we have done wickedly.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“O Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22005AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22005AP\"></sup>according to all your righteous acts, let your anger and your wrath turn away from your city Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22005AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22005AQ\"></sup>your holy hill, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22005AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22005AR\"></sup>because for our sins, and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22005AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22005AS\"></sup>the iniquities of our fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22005AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22005AT\"></sup>Jerusalem and your people have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22005AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22005AU\"></sup>a byword among all who are around us.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now therefore, O our God, listen to the prayer of your servant and to his pleas for mercy, and for your own sake, O Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22006AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22006AV\"></sup>make your face to shine upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22006AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22006AW\"></sup>your sanctuary, which is desolate.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22007AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22007AX\"></sup>O my God, incline your ear and hear. Open your eyes and see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22007AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22007AY\"></sup>our desolations, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22007AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22007AZ\"></sup>the city that is called by your name. For we do not present our pleas before you because of our righteousness, but because of your great mercy.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>O Lord, hear; O Lord, forgive. O Lord, pay attention and act. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22008BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22008BA\"></sup>Delay not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22008BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22008BB\"></sup>for your own sake, O my God, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22008BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22008BC\"></sup>your city and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22008BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22008BD\"></sup>your people are called by your name.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22009BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22009BE\"></sup>While I was speaking and praying, confessing my sin and the sin of my people Israel, and presenting my plea before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22009BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22009BF\"></sup>the holy hill of my God,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>while I was speaking in prayer, the man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22010BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22010BG\"></sup>Gabriel, whom I had seen in the vision at the first, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22010BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22010BH\"></sup>came to me in swift flight at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22010BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22010BI\"></sup>the time of the evening sacrifice.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22011BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22011BJ\"></sup>He made me understand, speaking with me and saying, “O Daniel, I have now come out to give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22011BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22011BK\"></sup>insight and understanding.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22012BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22012BL\"></sup>At the beginning of your pleas for mercy a word went out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22012BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22012BM\"></sup>and I have come to tell it to you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22012BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22012BN\"></sup>you are greatly loved. Therefore consider the word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22012BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22012BO\"></sup>and understand the vision.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22013BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22013BP\"></sup>“Seventy weeks are decreed about your people and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22013BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22013BQ\"></sup>your holy city, to finish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22013BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22013BR\"></sup>the transgression, to put an end to sin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22013BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22013BS\"></sup>and to atone for iniquity, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22013BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22013BT\"></sup>to bring in everlasting righteousness, to seal both vision and prophet, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22013BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22013BU\"></sup>to anoint a most holy place.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22014BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22014BV\"></sup>Know therefore and understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22014BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22014BW\"></sup>from the going out of the word to restore and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22014BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22014BX\"></sup>build Jerusalem to the coming of an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22014BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22014BY\"></sup>anointed one, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22014BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22014BZ\"></sup>prince, there shall be seven weeks. Then for sixty-two weeks it shall be built again with squares and moat, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22014CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22014CA\"></sup>but in a troubled time.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And after the sixty-two weeks, an anointed one shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22015CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22015CB\"></sup>be cut off and shall have nothing. And the people of the prince who is to come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22015CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22015CC\"></sup>shall destroy the city and the sanctuary. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22015CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22015CD\"></sup>Its end shall come with a flood, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22015CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22015CE\"></sup>and to the end there shall be war. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22015CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22015CF\"></sup>Desolations are decreed.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he shall make a strong covenant with many for one week, and for half of the week he shall put an end to sacrifice and offering. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22016CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22016CG\"></sup>And on the wing of abominations shall come one who makes desolate, until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22016CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22016CH\"></sup>the decreed end is poured out on the desolator.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22017A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22017A\"></sup>In the third year of Cyrus king of Persia a word was revealed to Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22017B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22017B\"></sup>who was named Belteshazzar. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22017C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22017C\"></sup>the word was true, and it was a great conflict. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22017D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22017D\"></sup>he understood the word and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22017E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22017E\"></sup>had understanding of the vision.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In those days I, Daniel, was mourning for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22018F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22018F\"></sup>three weeks.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I ate no delicacies, no meat or wine entered my mouth, nor did I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22019G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22019G\"></sup>anoint myself at all, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22019H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22019H\"></sup>the full three weeks.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>On the twenty-fourth day of the first month, as I was standing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22020I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22020I\"></sup>on the bank of the great river (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22020J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22020J\"></sup>that is, the Tigris)",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22021K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22021K\"></sup>I lifted up my eyes and looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22021L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22021L\"></sup>a man clothed in linen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22021M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22021M\"></sup>with a belt of fine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22021N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22021N\"></sup>gold from Uphaz around his waist.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>His body was like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22022O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22022O\"></sup>beryl, his face <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22022P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22022P\"></sup>like the appearance of lightning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22022Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22022Q\"></sup>his eyes like flaming torches, his arms and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22022R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22022R\"></sup>legs like the gleam of burnished bronze, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22022S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22022S\"></sup>the sound of his words like the sound of a multitude.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22023T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22023T\"></sup>And I, Daniel, alone saw the vision, for the men who were with me did not see the vision, but a great trembling fell upon them, and they fled to hide themselves.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So I was left alone and saw this great vision, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22024U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22024U\"></sup>no strength was left in me. My radiant appearance was fearfully changed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22024V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22024V\"></sup>and I retained no strength.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I heard the sound of his words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22025W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22025W\"></sup>and as I heard the sound of his words, I fell on my face in deep sleep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22025X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22025X\"></sup>with my face to the ground.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22026Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22026Y\"></sup>a hand touched me and set me trembling on my hands and knees.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he said to me, “O Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22027Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22027Z\"></sup>man greatly loved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22027AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22027AA\"></sup>understand the words that I speak to you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22027AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22027AB\"></sup>stand upright, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22027AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22027AC\"></sup>now I have been sent to you.” And when he had spoken this word to me, I stood up trembling.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22028AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22028AD\"></sup>“Fear not, Daniel, for from the first day that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22028AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22028AE\"></sup>set your heart to understand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22028AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22028AF\"></sup>humbled yourself before your God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22028AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22028AG\"></sup>your words have been heard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22028AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22028AH\"></sup>and I have come because of your words.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22029AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22029AI\"></sup>The prince of the kingdom of Persia withstood me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22029AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22029AJ\"></sup>twenty-one days, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22029AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22029AK\"></sup>Michael, one of the chief princes, came to help me, for I was left there with the kings of Persia,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22030AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22030AL\"></sup>and came to make you understand what is to happen to your people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22030AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22030AM\"></sup>in the latter days. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22030AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22030AN\"></sup>the vision is for days yet to come.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When he had spoken to me according to these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22031AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22031AO\"></sup>I turned my face toward the ground <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22031AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22031AP\"></sup>and was mute.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22032AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22032AQ\"></sup>one in the likeness of the children of man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22032AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22032AR\"></sup>touched my lips. Then I opened my mouth and spoke. I said to him who stood before me, “O my lord, by reason of the vision pains have come upon me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22032AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22032AS\"></sup>I retain no strength.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>How can my lord's servant talk with my lord? For now no strength remains in me, and no breath is left in me.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22034AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22034AT\"></sup>one having the appearance of a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22034AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22034AU\"></sup>touched me and strengthened me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22035AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22035AV\"></sup>“O man greatly loved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22035AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22035AW\"></sup>fear not, peace be with you; be strong and of good courage.” And as he spoke to me, I was strengthened and said, “Let my lord speak, for you have strengthened me.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then he said, “Do you know why I have come to you? But now I will return to fight against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22036AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22036AX\"></sup>prince of Persia; and when I go out, behold, the prince of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22036AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22036AY\"></sup>Greece will come.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But I will tell you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22037AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22037AZ\"></sup>what is inscribed in the book of truth: there is none who contends by my side against these except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22037BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22037BA\"></sup>Michael, your prince."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>“And as for me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22038A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22038A\"></sup>in the first year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22038B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22038B\"></sup>Darius the Mede, I stood up to confirm and strengthen him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“And now I will show you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22039C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22039C\"></sup>the truth. Behold, three more kings shall arise in Persia, and a fourth shall be far richer than all of them. And when he has become strong through his riches, he shall stir up all against the kingdom of Greece.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22040D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22040D\"></sup>a mighty king shall arise, who shall rule with great dominion and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22040E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22040E\"></sup>do as he wills.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And as soon as he has arisen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22041F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22041F\"></sup>his kingdom shall be broken and divided <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22041G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22041G\"></sup>toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22041H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22041H\"></sup>four winds of heaven, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22041I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22041I\"></sup>not to his posterity, nor according to the authority with which he ruled, for his kingdom shall be plucked up and go to others besides these.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Then the king of the south shall be strong, but one of his princes shall be stronger than he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22042J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22042J\"></sup>and shall rule, and his authority shall be a great authority.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>After some years <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22043K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22043K\"></sup>they shall make an alliance, and the daughter of the king of the south shall come to the king of the north to make an agreement. But she shall not retain the strength of her arm, and he and his arm shall not endure, but she shall be given up, and her attendants, he who fathered her, and he who supported her in those times.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And from a branch from her roots one shall arise in his place. He shall come against the army and enter the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22044L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22044L\"></sup>fortress of the king of the north, and he shall deal with them and shall prevail.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He shall also carry off to Egypt their gods with their metal images and their precious <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22045M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22045M\"></sup>vessels of silver and gold, and for some years he shall refrain from attacking the king of the north.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the latter shall come into the realm of the king of the south but shall return to his own land.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“His sons shall wage war and assemble a multitude of great forces, which shall keep coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22047N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22047N\"></sup>and overflow and pass through, and again shall carry the war as far as his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22047O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22047O\"></sup>fortress.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the king of the south, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22048P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22048P\"></sup>moved with rage, shall come out and fight against the king of the north. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22048Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22048Q\"></sup>And he shall raise a great multitude, but it shall be given into his hand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when the multitude is taken away, his heart shall be exalted, and he shall cast down tens of thousands, but he shall not prevail.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For the king of the north shall again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22050R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22050R\"></sup>raise a multitude, greater than the first. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22050S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22050S\"></sup>after some years he shall come on with a great army and abundant supplies.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“In those times many shall rise against the king of the south, and the violent among your own people shall lift themselves up in order to fulfill the vision, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22051T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22051T\"></sup>they shall fail.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the king of the north shall come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22052U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22052U\"></sup>throw up siegeworks and take a well-fortified city. And the forces of the south shall not stand, or even his best troops, for there shall be no strength to stand.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But he who comes against him shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22053V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22053V\"></sup>do as he wills, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22053W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22053W\"></sup>none shall stand before him. And he shall stand in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22053X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22053X\"></sup>the glorious land, with destruction in his hand.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22054Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22054Y\"></sup>set his face to come with the strength of his whole kingdom, and he shall bring terms of an agreement and perform them. He shall give him the daughter of women to destroy the kingdom, but it shall not stand or be to his advantage.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Afterward he shall turn his face to the coastlands and shall capture many of them, but a commander shall put an end to his insolence. Indeed, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22055Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22055Z\"></sup>shall turn his insolence back upon him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then he shall turn his face back toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22056AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22056AA\"></sup>fortresses of his own land, but he shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22056AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22056AB\"></sup>stumble and fall, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22056AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22056AC\"></sup>and shall not be found.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Then shall arise in his place one who shall send an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22057AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22057AD\"></sup>exactor of tribute for the glory of the kingdom. But within a few days he shall be broken, neither in anger nor in battle.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In his place shall arise a contemptible person to whom royal majesty has not been given. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22058AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22058AE\"></sup>He shall come in without warning and obtain the kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22058AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22058AF\"></sup>by flatteries.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Armies shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22059AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22059AG\"></sup>utterly swept away before him and broken, even the prince of the covenant.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And from the time that an alliance is made with him he shall act deceitfully, and he shall become strong with a small people.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22061AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22061AH\"></sup>Without warning he shall come into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22061AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22061AI\"></sup>the richest parts of the province, and he shall do what neither his fathers nor his fathers' fathers have done, scattering among them plunder, spoil, and goods. He shall devise plans against strongholds, but only for a time.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And he shall stir up his power and his heart against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22062AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22062AJ\"></sup>the king of the south with a great army. And the king of the south shall wage war with an exceedingly great and mighty army, but he shall not stand, for plots shall be devised against him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Even those who eat his food shall break him. His army shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22063AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22063AK\"></sup>swept away, and many shall fall down slain.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And as for the two kings, their hearts shall be bent on doing evil. They shall speak lies at the same table, but to no avail, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22064AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22064AL\"></sup>the end is yet to be at the time appointed.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he shall return to his land with great wealth, but his heart shall be set against the holy covenant. And he shall work his will and return to his own land.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“At the time appointed he shall return and come into the south, but it shall not be this time as it was before.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For ships of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22067AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22067AM\"></sup>Kittim shall come against him, and he shall be afraid and withdraw, and shall turn back and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22067AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22067AN\"></sup>be enraged and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22067AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22067AO\"></sup>take action against the holy covenant. He shall turn back and pay attention to those who forsake the holy covenant.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Forces from him shall appear and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22068AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22068AP\"></sup>profane the temple and fortress, and shall take away the regular burnt offering. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22068AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22068AQ\"></sup>they shall set up the abomination that makes desolate.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He shall seduce with flattery those who violate the covenant, but the people who know their God shall stand firm and take action.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22070AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22070AR\"></sup>And the wise among the people shall make many understand, though for some days they shall stumble by sword and flame, by captivity and plunder.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>When they stumble, they shall receive a little help. And many shall join themselves to them with flattery,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>and some of the wise shall stumble, so that they may be refined, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22072AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22072AS\"></sup>purified, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22072AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22072AT\"></sup>made white, until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22072AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22072AU\"></sup>the time of the end, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22072AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22072AV\"></sup>for it still awaits the appointed time.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“And the king shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22073AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22073AW\"></sup>do as he wills. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22073AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22073AX\"></sup>He shall exalt himself and magnify himself above every god, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22073AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22073AY\"></sup>and shall speak astonishing things against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22073AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22073AZ\"></sup>the God of gods. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22073BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22073BA\"></sup>He shall prosper <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22073BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22073BB\"></sup>till the indignation is accomplished; for what is decreed shall be done.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>He shall pay no attention to the gods of his fathers, or to the one beloved by women. He shall not pay attention to any other god, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22074BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22074BC\"></sup>he shall magnify himself above all.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>He shall honor the god of fortresses instead of these. A god whom his fathers did not know he shall honor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22075BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22075BD\"></sup>with gold and silver, with precious stones and costly gifts.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>He shall deal with the strongest fortresses with the help of a foreign god. Those who acknowledge him he shall load with honor. He shall make them rulers over many and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22076BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22076BE\"></sup>shall divide the land for a price.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22077BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22077BF\"></sup>“At the time of the end, the king of the south shall attack him, but the king of the north shall rush upon him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22077BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22077BG\"></sup>like a whirlwind, with chariots and horsemen, and with many ships. And he shall come into countries and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22077BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22077BH\"></sup>shall overflow and pass through.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>He shall come into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22078BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22078BI\"></sup>the glorious land. And tens of thousands shall fall, but these shall be delivered out of his hand: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22078BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22078BJ\"></sup>Edom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22078BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22078BK\"></sup>Moab and the main part of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22078BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22078BL\"></sup>Ammonites.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>He shall stretch out his hand against the countries, and the land of Egypt shall not escape.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>He shall become ruler of the treasures of gold and of silver, and all the precious things of Egypt, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22080BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22080BM\"></sup>Libyans and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22080BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22080BN\"></sup>Cushites shall follow in his train.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>But news from the east and the north shall alarm him, and he shall go out with great fury to destroy and devote many to destruction.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And he shall pitch his palatial tents between the sea and the glorious holy mountain. Yet he shall come to his end, with none to help him."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>“At that time shall arise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22083A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22083A\"></sup>Michael, the great prince who has charge of your people. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22083B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22083B\"></sup>there shall be a time of trouble, such as never has been since there was a nation till that time. But at that time your people shall be delivered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22083C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22083C\"></sup>everyone whose name shall be found written in the book.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And many of those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22084D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22084D\"></sup>sleep in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22084E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22084E\"></sup>the dust of the earth shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22084F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22084F\"></sup>awake, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22084G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22084G\"></sup>some to everlasting life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22084H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22084H\"></sup>some to shame and everlasting contempt.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22085I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22085I\"></sup>And those who are wise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22085J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22085J\"></sup>shall shine like the brightness of the sky above; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22085K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22085K\"></sup>those who turn many to righteousness, like the stars forever and ever.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But you, Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22086L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22086L\"></sup>shut up the words and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22086M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22086M\"></sup>seal the book, until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22086N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22086N\"></sup>the time of the end. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22086O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22086O\"></sup>Many shall run to and fro, and knowledge shall increase.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I, Daniel, looked, and behold, two others stood, one on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22087P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22087P\"></sup>this bank of the stream and one on that bank of the stream.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And someone said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22088Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22088Q\"></sup>the man clothed in linen, who was above the waters of the stream, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22088R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22088R\"></sup>“How long shall it be till the end of these wonders?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22089S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22089S\"></sup>the man clothed in linen, who was above the waters of the stream; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22089T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22089T\"></sup>he raised his right hand and his left hand toward heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22089U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22089U\"></sup>swore by him who lives forever that it would be for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22089V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22089V\"></sup>time, times, and half a time, and that when the shattering of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22089W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22089W\"></sup>the power of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22089X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22089X\"></sup>the holy people comes to an end all these things would be finished.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I heard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22090Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22090Y\"></sup>but I did not understand. Then I said, “O my lord, what shall be the outcome of these things?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22091Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22091Z\"></sup>“Go your way, Daniel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22091AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22091AA\"></sup>for the words are shut up and sealed until the time of the end.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22092AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22092AB\"></sup>Many shall purify themselves and make themselves white and be refined, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22092AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22092AC\"></sup>the wicked shall act wickedly. And none of the wicked shall understand, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22092AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22092AD\"></sup>but those who are wise shall understand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And from the time that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22093AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22093AE\"></sup>the regular burnt offering is taken away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22093AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22093AF\"></sup>the abomination that makes desolate is set up, there shall be 1,290 days.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22094AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22094AG\"></sup>Blessed is he who waits and arrives at the 1,335 days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22095AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22095AH\"></sup>But go your way till the end. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22095AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22095AI\"></sup>And you shall rest and shall stand in your allotted place at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22095AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22095AJ\"></sup>the end of the days.”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;